    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition at $34,000, and that description is accurate and honest. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains good color and shine, though you'll notice some light surface scratches and minor wear consistent with regular use. There are no major dents or structural damage, but it's not a showroom-perfect vehicle either. The interior is clean and functional, with normal wear on the seats and trim that you'd expect from a well-used car. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably and has been maintained, though as with any used car in this condition, a pre-purchase inspection is always a smart idea. What you're getting is a solid, dependable vehicle at a fair price \u2014 not flawless, but genuinely good and ready for everyday driving.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and buyers should have realistic expectations before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust, dents, and paint deterioration in multiple areas. The interior has considerable wear with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle or someone needing basic transportation on a tight budget. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. Priced accordingly to reflect the true condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
