      "description": "This vehicle is listed in good condition, and that is a straightforward, honest assessment. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains most of its original luster with only minor surface blemishes and light scratches consistent with normal everyday use. You won't find deep dents or significant body damage here, just the honest marks of a car that has been driven and reasonably cared for. The interior is clean and functional: upholstery shows moderate wear in the expected high-contact areas, but there are no tears, stains, or broken components to report. Mechanically, this car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts promptly, transmission shifts smoothly, and all primary systems are in proper working order. There are no warning lights on the dash, and the car has been maintained with regular servicing. Tires have adequate tread remaining, and brakes are in acceptable condition. This is a solid, dependable used vehicle that will serve a buyer well without requiring immediate repairs \u2014 priced fairly to reflect its true, good-condition status.",
